metadata.name: SBPxJarutis #1
metadata.description: A collaboration between creative gang "Sick Block Party" and music artist Justinas Jarutis. 111 NFTs are divided into parts of the song that will be unclocked and publicly released after the project reaches 100% goal. All funds will be donated to Ukrainian humanitarian organizations. [Check out our website.](https://sickblockparty.com/jarutis/)
